1. Start the 'Zookeeper Server' by using below command

	CMD:	.\bin\windows\zookeeper-server-start.bat .\config\zookeeper.properties

2. Start the 'Kafka-Server' using below commad

	CMD:	.\bin\windows\kafka-server-start.bat .\config\server.properties

3. Implement the Kafka-Application
	> Run the Application
	> Make the Request

4. Enter below command to View Topics in the Kafka Server

	CMD:	.\bin\windows\kafka-console-consumer.bat --topic order-topic1 --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

5. Implement the Kafka-Consumer Code
	> Will get Producer-Response in the Consumer Console window
	
